20a%20US%20Air%20Force%20aircraft%20had%20a%20near%20miss%20near%20Ronald%20Reagan%20Washington%20National%20Airport%2C%20just%20two%20months%20after%20a%20midair%20collision%20near%20the%20same%20airport%20killed%20more%20than%2060%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20on%20Friday%2C%20March%2028%2C%20at%203%3A16%20p.m.%20when%20Delta%20Flight%202983%2C%20an%20Airbus%20A319%2C%20had%20just%20received%20takeoff%20clearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20four%20US%20Air%20Force%20T-38%20Talons%20were%20inbound%20to%20Arlington%20National%20Cemetery%20for%20a%20flyover.%20The%20T-38%20Talon%20is%20a%20two-seat%20supersonic%20jet%20used%20to%20train%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fstatements%2Faccident_incidents%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Aviation%20Administration%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Delta%20pilot%20received%20an%20onboard%20alert%20that%20another%20aircraft%20was%20nearby.%20Air%20traffic%20controllers%20quickly%20issued%20corrective%20instructions%20to%20both%20planes%2C%20preventing%20a%20collision.%20The%20FAA%20has%20launched%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight%20tracking%20footage%20and%20audio%20communications%2C%20shared%20by%20VASAviation%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbPQjQ23YTJo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20show%20just%20how%20close%20the%20two%20aircraft%20came.%20Both%20flights%20continued%20to%20their%20destinations%20without%20further%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20more%20important%20than%20the%20safety%20of%20our%20customers%20and%20people.%20That's%20why%20the%20flight%20crew%20followed%20procedures%20to%20maneuver%20the%20aircraft%20as%20instructed%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Delta%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20near-miss%20incident%20came%20almost%20exactly%20two%20months%20after%20an%20American%20Airlines%20flight%20collided%20with%20a%20Black%20Hawk%20helicopter%20close%20to%20the%20same%20airport%2C%20killing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-subsidiary-plane-psa-crashes-potomac-river-dc-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E67%20people%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERonald%20Reagan%20Washington%20National%20Airport%2C%20located%20just%20outside%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20is%20home%20to%20the%20country's%20busiest%20runway%2C%20with%20over%20800%20takeoffs%20and%20landings%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airport%20is%20the%20closest%20of%20three%20area%20airports%20to%20the%20city%2C%20about%203%20miles%20south%20of%20the%20White%20House.%20Its%20proximity%20to%20Capitol%20Hill%20makes%20it%20a%20favorite%20of%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilitary%20helicopters%20also%20frequently%20fly%20low%20over%20the%20nearby%20Potomac%20River%2C%20transiting%20between%20military%20bases%20close%20by%20and%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20about%20a%20mile%20north%20of%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlying%20into%20and%20out%20of%20Reagan%20Airport%2C%20with%20short%20runways%20and%20such%20heavily%20restricted%20airspace%20nearby%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Blike%20threading%20a%20needle%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20pilot%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20January%20incident%2C%20Brian%20Alexander%2C%20a%20military%20helicopter%20pilot%20and%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20aviation%20accident%20law%20firm%20Kreindler%20%26amp%3B%20Kreindler%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdc-plane-crash-aviation-experts-long-feared-nightmare-scenario-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshortage%20of%20air%20traffic%20controllers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20increasing%20airspace%20congestion%20had%20affected%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20whole%20air%20traffic%20control%20system%20has%20been%20blinking%20red%2C%20screaming%20at%20us%20that%20we've%20got%20it%20overloaded%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20broadly%2C%20air%20traffic%20congestion%20has%20become%20a%20growing%20concern.%20According%20to%20a%20January%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntsb.gov%2Finvestigations%2FDocuments%2FDCA25MA108%2520Prelim.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%2C%20there%20were%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20close%20calls%20between%20commercial%20airplanes%20and%20helicopters%20from%20October%202021%20to%20December%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-air-lines-air-force-involved-near-miss-incident-dc-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743418111000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ea5ca969253ccddf9ab9bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-air-lines-air-force-involved-near-miss-incident-dc-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20January%2C%20an%20American%20Airlines%20plane%20and%20a%20military%20helicopter%20collided%20near%20the%20same%20airport%2C%20killing%20more%20than%2060%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelta-air-lines-air-force-involved-near-miss-incident-dc-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sanoj%20Mishra%2C%20who%20offered%20to%20Monalisa%2C%20arrested%20for%20alleged%20rape%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743417834000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119802877%2Cimgsize-45568.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffilmmaker-sanoj-mishra-who-offered-a-film-to-maha-kumbh-viral-girl-monalisa-arrested-for