ble%20to%20shake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20miss%20living%20a%20short%2020%20to%2030-minute%20drive%20from%20our%20family%20who%20are%20still%20in%20Jersey.%20And%20while%20the%20small%20village%20we%20live%20near%20is%20nice%2C%20it's%20just%20that%20%E2%80%94%20small.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20prefer%20being%20closer%20to%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20New%20York%20City%20with%20its%20diverse%20neighborhoods%2C%20major%20museums%2C%20and%20vibrant%20theater%20and%20music%20scenes%2C%20all%20of%20which%20we%20frequented%20often%20while%20in%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20realized%20we%20weren't%20the%20beach%20lovers%20we%20thought%20we%20were.%20Going%20to%20the%20beach%20had%20once%20been%20a%20treat.%20Now%2C%20we%20easily%20take%20it%20for%20granted%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20less%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20traffic%20jams%20and%20packed%20beaches%20in%20season%20make%20getting%20there%20a%20headache%20and%20a%20sweaty%20nailbiter%2C%20with%20parking%20lots%20at%20capacity%20by%208%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20noise%2C%20the%20grind%20of%20cars%2C%20and%20the%20lines%20snaking%20out%20of%20seemingly%20every%20coffee%20bar%20and%20lunch%20spot%20conspire%20to%20make%20a%20summer%20day%20about%20as%20relaxing%20as%20a%20full-throttle%20city%20commute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20miss%20our%20hikes%20through%20the%20small%20mountain%20range%20that%20was%20minutes%20away%20from%20our%20NJ%20house.%20The%20flat%2C%20bleached%20terrain%20without%20a%20hill%20in%20sight%20just%20isn't%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20that%20outdoorsy%20experience%20now%2C%20we%20must%20drive%2090%20minutes%20north%2C%20on%20a%20dismal%2C%20nerve-jangling%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf3ee217-b2b9-4ea0-a449-9905237031bc%5C%22%3EWe%20feel%20like%20part%20of%20a%20community%20here%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20greatest%20gift%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWelcome%20mats%20for%20pickleball%20teams%2C%20girls'%20nights%2C%20potlucks%2C%20and%20a%20d