ger.%20Then%20it%20was%20to%20break%20into%20fintech%20as%20a%20business%20analyst.%20But%20during%20his%20sophomore%20and%20junior%20years%2C%20as%20the%20tech%20industry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-jobs-recession-layoffs-gen-z-students-class-of-2023-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20nearly%20half%20a%20million%20workers%2C%20Kim%20struggled%20to%20secure%20an%20internship.%20So%20he%20set%20his%20eyes%20on%20a%20new%20career%3A%20public%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20was%20far%20from%20the%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-hot-jobs-tech-layoffs-healthcare-government-careers-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGen%20Zer%3C%2Fa%3E%20making%20the%20same%20pivot.%20Last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20job%20site%20Handshake%2C%20the%20share%20of%20applications%20it%20received%20from%20college%20seniors%20for%20entry-level%20openings%20in%20tech%20dropped%20by%2019%25%20from%202022%2C%20while%20the%20share%20to%20jobs%20in%20government%20nearly%20doubled.%20Even%20younger%20kids%20saw%20the%20writing%20on%20the%20wall.%20In%20surveys%2C%20high%20school%20students%20used%20to%20cite%20tech%20giants%20like%20Google%20and%20Apple%20as%20the%20places%20they%20most%20wanted%20to%20work.%20But%20last%20year%2C%20in%20a%20startling%20shift%2C%20both%20the%20FBI%20and%20NASA%20ranked%20higher%20than%20any%20of%20those%20tech%20companies.%20Silicon%20Valley%20was%20out.%20Capitol%20Hill%20was%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Kim%20only%20a%20single%20application%20to%20land%20a%20yearlong%20paid%20internship%20at%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration.%20His%20performance%20reviews%20were%20good%2C%20and%20he%20planned%20to%20stay%20on%20at%20the%20agency%20after%20he%20earned%20his%20degree%20in%20May.%20%26quot%3BYou%20hear%20so%20many%20horror%20stories%20of%20people%20in%20tech%20being%20laid%20off%20with%20little%20notice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BGovernment%20jobs%20are%20secure.%20What%20drew%20me%20into%20it%20was%20the%20stability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20for%20that%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20month%2C%20with%20his%20graduation%20fast%20approaching%2C%20Kim%20abruptly%20lost%20his%20internship%20amid%20the%20government-wide%20havoc%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20unleashed%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20most%20federal%20hiring%20on%20an%20indefinite%20hold%2C%20he's%20been%20scrambling%20to%20find%20a%20job%20%E2%80%94%20any%20job.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20a%20huge%20source%20of%20stress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20private%20industry%20has%20already%20hired%20their%20graduating%20students.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKim%20is%20one%20of%20the%20roughly%202%20million%20students%20set%20to%20graduate%20this%20spring%20into%20an%20exceptionally%20shaky%20job%20market.%20Things%20were%20already%20looking%20tough%20for%20the%20class%20of%202025%2C%20given%20the%20steep%20hiring%20slump%20in%20industries%20like%20tech%2C%20finance%2C%20and%20consulting.%20But%20now%2C%20as%20Musk%20takes%20a%20chainsaw%20to%20the%20government%2C%20many%20college%20seniors%20are%20in%20panic%20mode.%20Some%20have%20seen%20their%20offers%20at%20federal%20agencies%20rescinded%3B%20others%20have%20received%20no%20word%20on%20jobs%20they%20applied%20to%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20government%20positions%20that%20are%20taking%20a%20hit%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20jobs%20at%20a%20whole%20host%20of%20businesses%2C%20nonprofits%2C%20and%20universities%20that%20rely%20on%20federal%20funding%20and%20contracts.%20And%20going%20to%20graduate%20school%20%E2%80%94%20the%20traditional%20backup%20plan%20for%20students%20during%20times%20of%20economic%20instability%20%E2%80%94%20may%20not%20even%20be%20an%20option%2C%20if%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20winds%20up%20being%20unable%20to%20deliver%20financial%20aid%20in%20a%20timely%20fashion.%20As%20the%20government%20is%20slashed%20to%20the%20bone%20in%20the%20name%20of%20efficiency%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-employee-engagement-workplace-morale-careers-boomers-gen-x-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareers%20of%20many%20Gen%20Zers%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20suffer%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20impact%20is%20broad%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Saskia%20Campbell%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20university%20career%20services%20at%20George%20Mason%20University.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20this%20sense%20of%20grief%2C%20of%20loss%20of%20opportunity.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20year%20I'm%20actually%20concerned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20the%20outlook%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20even%20more%20dismal%20in%20the%20months%20ahead%2C%20as%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20tariff%20wars%20spur%20companies%20to%20hold%20off%20on%20hiring.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20uncertainty%20and%20fear%20was%20in%20Big%20Tech%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Briana%20Randall%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20career%20and%20internship%20center%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Washington.%20%26quot%3BNow%20it%20feels%20uncertain%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20that%20leaves%20America's%20soon-to-be%20new%20grads%20unsure%20of%20where%20to%20turn.%20Sarina%20Parsapasand%2C%20a%20public%20policy%20major%20who's%20graduating%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%20this%20spring%2C%20was%20hoping%20to%20land%20a%20job%20in%20government%20service.%20But%20now%2C%20given%20the%20chaos%20in%20Washington%2C%20she's%20switched%20to%20trying%20to%20land%20a%20job%20in%20the%20private%20sector.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20bills%20to%20pay%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20take%20the%20risk%20of%20being%20in%20a%20job%20that%20doesn't%20guarantee%20the%20stability%20for%20me%20to%20live%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20sentiment%20I%20hear%20over%20and%20over%20again%20from%20the%20students%20I%20speak%20with.%20%26quot%3BThe%20job%20market%20just%20seems%20super%20unstable%20in%20almost%20any%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Katie%20Schwartz%2C%20a%20sophomore%20at%20Tulane.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20less%20about%20finding%20a%20job%20you%20really%20love%20now%20and%20more%20just%20about%20finding%20a%20job%20that's%20going%20to%20give%20you%20job%20stability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20impressed%20by%20the%20clear-eyed%20pragmatism%20of%20these%20students%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'm%20also%20saddened%20by%20how%20%3Cem%3Eold%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethey%20sound.%20Isn't%20job%20stability%20what%20you%20look%20for%20when%20you're%20middle-aged%2C%20with%20a%20mortgage%20to%20pay%20and%20kids%20to%20support%3F%20When%20I%20graduated%20from%20college%20in%202009%20without%20a%20full-time%20job%2C%20I%20was%20panicked%20but%20still%20idealistic.%20These%20kids%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20seem%20hardened%20by%20all%20the%20chaos%20they've%20endured%20from%20a%20young%20age.%20In%20high%20school%2C%20they%20watched%20their%20parents%20get%20laid%20off%20in%20the%20pandemic.%20In%20college%2C%20they%20watched%20older%20students%20struggle%20to%20land%20good%20jobs%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-collar-recession-hiring-slump-jobs-tech-industry-applications-rejection-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20downturn%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%20worse%2C%20had%20their%20hard-won%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-college-students-renege-job-offers-tech-rescinded-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffers%20rescinded%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20upheaval%20and%20uncertainty%20have%20taught%20today's%20graduates%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20worst.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20one%20college%20senior%20tells%20me%2C%20she's%20been%20intentionally%20neglecting%20her%20studies%20so%20she%20could%20focus%20exclusively%20on%20her%20job%20search%2C%20sending%20out%20as%20many%20as%2015%20applications%20a%20day.%20The%20hustle%20paid%20off%20with%20three%20offers%2C%20including%20one%20she%20accepted%20from%20a%20government%20contractor.%20It's%20her%20%26quot%3Bdream%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20because%20it%20would%20enable%20her%20to%20make%20a%20real%20difference%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20given%20the%20chaos%20in%20Washington%2C%20she's%20leaning%20toward%20reneging%20on%20the%20offer%20and%20accepting%20a%20position%20at%20a%20finance%20company.%20(That's%20why%20she%20asked%20me%20not%20to%20use%20her%20name.)%20%26quot%3BI%20try%20to%20keep%20an%20optimistic%20outlook%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%20But%20when%20I%20ask%20her%20how%20she%20feels%20about%20taking%20her%20first%20steps%20into%20adulthood%2C%20she%20doesn't%20sound%20optimistic%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20me%20pretty%20nervous%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20my%20generation%20have%20accepted%20that%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20live%20the%20same%20quality%20of%20life%20our%20parents%20provided%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20hard%20economic%20times%2C%20we%20expect%20to%20hear%20stories%20about%20people%20losing%20their%20jobs.%20But%20the%20greatest%20casualties%20often%20end%20up%20being%20the%20young%20people%20who%20don't%20have%20jobs%20to%20lose%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20Hiring%20freezes%20hurt%20them%20the%20most%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20for%20them%20to%20even%20get%20their%20foot%20in%20the%20door.%20And%20research%20shows%20just%20how%20long%20a%20shadow%20that%20can%20cast%20on%20someone's%20career.%20Five%20years%20after%20the%20Great%20Recession%2C%20my%20generation%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-is-the-luckiest-generation-vs-millennials%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillennials%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20earning%2011%25%20less%20than%20Gen%20Xers%20were%20at%20a%20comparable%20age.%20And%20our%20net%20worth%20fell%2040%25%20behind%20theirs%2C%20forcing%20us%20to%20delay%20many%20of%20life's%20biggest%20milestones%3A%20buying%20a%20home%2C%20starting%20a%20family%2C%20saving%20for%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effects%20go%20far%20beyond%20money.%20Students%20who%20graduated%20into%20the%201982%20recession%2C%20for%20example%2C%20wound%20up%20with%20fewer%20kids%20and%20more%20divorces%20than%20those%20who%20entered%20better%20job%20markets.%20Even%20more%20shocking%2C%20the%20research%20shows%2C%20they%20were%20more%20likely%20to%20die%20early.%20Whatever%20gains%20in%20efficiency%20Trump%20hopes%20to%20achieve%20from%20DOGE%2C%20its%20most%20lasting%20legacy%20may%20end%20up%20being%20the%20harm%20it%20inflicts%20on%20the%20careers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20perhaps%20even%20the%20life%20spans%20%E2%80%94%20of%20his%20youngest%20constituents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20leaves%20college%20seniors%20like%20Kim%20scrambling%20to%20find%20a%20foothold%20in%20a%20job%20market%20that%20is%20stacked%20against%20them.%20Many%20companies%20have%20already%20filled%20their%20entry-level%20positions%2C%20if%20they're%20hiring%20new%20grads%20at%20all.%20And%20he's%20now%20competing%20not%20only%20with%20his%20fellow%20students%2C%20but%20also%20with%20the%20flood%20of%20young%20government%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20laid%20off%20by%20DOGE%20%E2%80%94%20workers%20who%20have%20more%20experience%20than%20he%20does.%20As%20graduation%20nears%2C%20he's%20trying%20not%20to%20panic.%20But%20it's%20hard%20to%20retain%20a%20sense%20of%20hope%20when%20even%20lower-paying%20jobs%20in%20public%20service%20are%20no%20longer%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20how%20my%20future's%20going%20to%20turn%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Kim%20tells%20me.%20And%20that%2C%20when%20you%20think%20about%20it%2C%20is%20a%20future%20that%20should%20worry%20us%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Faki-ito%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAki%20Ito%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20chief%20correspondent%20for%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-damage-gen-z-careers-tech-layoffs-job-market-hiring-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743408241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e6e8e863d72727e1989416%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-damage-gen-z-careers-tech-layoffs-job-market-hiring-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Between%20tech%20layoffs%20and%20DOGE%20cuts%2C%20college%20students%20are%20running%20out%20of%20job%20prospects%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20could%20haunt%20them%20for%20years%20to%20come%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aito%40businessinsider.com%20(Aki%20Ito)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-damage-gen-z-careers-tech-layoffs-job-market-hiring-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%8BBarkha%20Bisht%20alleges%20ex-husband%20Indraneil%20of%20infedility%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743407606000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119796286%2Cimgsize-20002.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbarkha-bisht-opens-up-on-ex-husband-indraneil-senguptas-alleged-infidelity-the-worst-thing-you-can-do-to-a-woman%2Farticleshow%2F119794662.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https