er%20Greenland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20semiautonomous%20territory%20of%20Denmark%2C%20arguing%20the%20island%20is%20needed%20to%20bolster%20US%20security%20and%20its%20stocks%20of%20strategic%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20joint%20address%20to%20Congress%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20president%20said%20the%20United%20States%20would%20take%20control%20of%20Greenland%20%26quot%3Bone%20way%20or%20the%20other.%26quot%3B%20And%20recently%2C%20Trump%20declined%20to%20rule%20out%20military%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Usha%2C%20arrived%20in%20Greenland%20on%20Friday%2C%20embarking%20on%20a%20scaled-back%20trip%20that%20included%20a%20stop%20at%20the%20US-operated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreenland-us-military-base-photos-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPituffik%20Space%20Base%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20island's%20northwest%20coast.%20But%20even%20before%20the%20US%20delegation%20arrived%2C%20they%20were%20met%20with%20broad%20opposition%20to%20Trump's%20annexation%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20why%20the%20United%20States%20has%20shown%20so%20much%20interest%20in%20Greenland%20amid%20the%20territory's%20own%20push%20for%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Greenlanders%20are%20overwhelmingly%20opposed%20to%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%20US.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e9b8bc63d72727e198a9e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGreenland%20is%20overwhelmingly%20opposed%20to%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3Cp%3ECHRISTIAN%20KLINDT%20SOELBECK%2FRitzau%20Scanpix%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225efc0709-8ea7-43d1-8066-88a29f3e61c7%5C%22%3E'We%20have%20to%20have%20it'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Vance's%20trip%20to%20Greenland%2C%20Trump%20said%20the%20island%20