yle%20of%20art%20is%20found%20in%20the%20textile%20industry%20and%20like%20Amar%20Chitra%20Katha%2C%20Kalamkari%20to%20depicts%20mythology%20and%20nature.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIts%20origin%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalamkari%E2%80%99s%20roots%20date%20back%20to%20around%203000%20years%20ago%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana.%20This%20form%20of%20art%20was%20initially%20used%20by%20musicians%20and%20painters%20to%20narrate%20mythological%20stories%20on%20huge%20canvas.%20These%20canvases%20were%20found%20in%20temples%20usually.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20its%20used%20today%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20today%2C%20this%20art%20form%20is%20considered%20as%20a%20top%20pick%20among%20buyers.%20Thanks%20to%20its%20intricate%20designs%20and%20natural%20dyes%20that%20make%20it%20look%20bright%20and%20vibrant%20on%20fabrics.%20Today%2C%20there%20are%20two%20types%20of%20Kalamkaris%3A%20Srikalahasti%20and%20Machilipatnam.%20Srikalahasti%20style%20depicts%20free-hand%20paintings%2C%20while%20Machilipatnam%20is%20block-printng.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERaja%20Ravi%20verma%20painting%20style%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhibli%20might%20be%20cool%2C%20yes.%20But%20how%20about%20having%20an%20image%20generated%20in%20Raja%20Ravi%20Verma%E2%80%99s%20style.%20Classy%20would%20be%20the%20right%20word.%20Raja%20Ravi%20Verma%20paintings%20have%20always%20depicted%20South%20Indian%20women%20in%20the%20European%20academy%20art%20style.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIts%20origin%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaja%20Ravi%20Verma%20was%20born%20in%20Kilimanoor%2C%C2%A0%20Travancore.%20His%20talent%20in%20art%20was%20recognised%20and%20encouraged%20by%20his%20maternal%20uncle.%20Sri%20Chithra%20Art%20gallery%20where%20Raja%20Ravi%20Verma%E2%80%99s%20paintings%20are%20exhibited%20was%20started%20in%201935%20to%20develop%20the%20taste%20of%20art%20among%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20its%20used%20today%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20iconic%20paintings%20today%20are%20used%20as%20framed%20prints%2C%20for%20calendars%20and%20posters%20and%20at%20religious%20centres%20to%20depict%20Hindu%20deities%20and%20mythological%20figures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20continues%20to%20shape%20the%20art%20world%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20not%20forget%20the%20beauty%20of%20hand-crafted%20traditions.%20Instead%20of%20simply%20following%20the%20latest%20trends%2C%20why%20not%20explore%20and%20support%20India%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20artistic%20heritage%3F%20The%20next%20time%20you%20admire%20an%20AI-generated%20piece%2C%20take%20a%20moment%20to%20discover%20the%20real%20artists%20and%20styles%20that%20have%20been%20shaping%20our%20culture%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743399229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FTBI-featured-image-7_11zon-1743397813.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D417095%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ghibli-style%20AI%20art%20is%20flooding%20social%20media%2C%20catching%20the%20attention%20of%20many.%20Beyond%20this%20trend%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20art%20forms%E2%80%94Madhubani%2C%20Kalamkari%2C%20and%20more%E2%80%94offer%20a%20world%20of%20colour%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20history.%20These%20centuries-old%20styles%20have%20long%20blended%20storytelling%20with%20artistry%2C%20each%20carrying%20its%20own%20unique%20heritage%20and%20visual%20appeal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F417095%2Fghibli-ai-art-is-viral-but-can-you-recognise-these-stunning-indian-art-stylesai-studio-ghibli-anime-chatgpt-artists-india-gemini%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20says%20'golden%20age'%20of%20US-India%